    (type::MonStgElt, d::RngIntElt, q::RngIntElt) -> SeqEnum, SeqEnum
    [
        Rewrite
    ]

        Unipotent conjugacy classes and their labels for the classical group of supplied 
        type, rank and field size.

e.g. 
U, UL := UnipotentClasses ("SU", 7, 3);
#U;

